title: Domino’s Pizza expands reach with ONDC entry
description: Sameer Khetarpal, managing director at JFL said the partnership with the ONDC Network is a “significant milestone and step forward” for Domino’s. T Koshy, managing director at ONDC said Domino’s joining ONDC “is a significant development with the potential to create ripple effects for the foods and beverages category on Open Network.
